  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968980/extras/349158dc14d80673c5c5f3eed616424e.avif?t=1643380501\" width=600 height=340 /></span><br><br>Dive into a real Christmas tale with a bright coloring puzzle Glass Painting: Winter Art. Create unique stained glass windows using a rich color palette, enjoy various visual effects: sunlight, glare, frost patterns, snowfall. Master the skills of harmonious combination of landscape and stained glass. Fill in all available stained glass windows and unlock new ones!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968980/extras/3c407b5ce27adb7974d715518477f608.avif?t=1643380501\" width=600 height=340 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>colorful winter clicker arcade with puzzle elements;<br></li><li>stained glass patterns;<br></li><li>bright color palette;<br></li><li>visual effects: sunlight, snow, glare, frost patterns, etc.;<br></li><li>several levels;<br></li><li>unique landscape creation;<br></li><li>sharing function.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968980/extras/6e8f2424dc6434445e5b58f3f0cca154.avif?t=1643380501\" width=600 height=340 /></span>",
